<h2><%= @tool['title'] %> - Histogram view</h2> 
<p> 

<div class="row">
<a name="General"></a>
<h3 class="<%= @section["name"] %>">General Remarks</h3>
<p>The histogram view consists of three sections: 
<ol>
  <li>A <b>Bar Diagram</b>, summarizing the positions and color-coded significances of the
database matches with more than 40% probability.</li>
  <li>A tabular <b>Hit List</b> with probabilities, E-values, scores, and match
regions in query and templates.</li>
  <li>The pairwise <b>HMM-HMM Alignments</b>, depicted as histograms over the amino acid distributions 
in the columns of the underlying multiple alignments. </li>
</ol>
The first two sections are described in detail on the
<a href="#" title="HHpred help on results" onclick="openHelpWindow('help_results');">Results</a> page of this help.
</p><br>

<div class="row">
